4月22日
张蒙蒙、高嵩进行课题组数据收集，待收集好后由郭望龙进行汇总并制作课题组网站

数据收集包括：
1.课题组简介
2.科研成果（发表论文、国家专利）
3.组内成员（成员介绍、研究方向）
4.人才培养
5.联系方式

4月25日 郭望龙提交科研成果相关信息

发表论文
1. Yi Wu, Zongwei Wang, Ziyu Xue, Yuhang Yan, Bushra Huma, Yuqian Zhou and Zhongxin Tan*. Fertilization of potentially toxic element-contaminated soils remediated with reusable biochar pellets using rice straw, pig manure and their derived biochar. Environmental Pollution, 2025, 366: 125551. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 8.3) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.envpol.2024.125551
2. Zongwei Wang, Yifan Dong, Tuo Zhou, Yi Wu and Zhongxin* Tan. Exploring the mechanism of removing Cd from polluted soil using electrochemical leaching with straw carbon film electrode. Journal of Environmental Chemical Engineering, 2024, 12: 114143. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 7.3) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jece.2024.113143
3. Zongwei Wang, Tuo Zhou, Jing Dai, Wantong Zhao and Zhongxin* Tan. A biochar electrode based on conductive straw for Cd removal and recovery from wastewater by DC electrochemical deposition. Biomass and Bioenergy, 2024, 189: 107347. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 5.2) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.biombioe.2024.107347
4. Yi Wu, Yuhang Yan, Zongwei Wang, Zhongxin Tan* and Tuo Zhou. Biochar application for the remediation of soil contaminated with potentially toxic elements: Current situation and challenges. Journal of Environmental Management, 2024, 351: 119775. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 7.9) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jenvman.2023.119775
5. Yi Wu, Zongwei Wang, Yuhang Yan, Yuqian Zhou, Bushra Huma, Zhongxin Tan* and Tuo Zhou. Recovery and regeneration of water-hardened magnetic composite biochar sphere for the removal of multiple heavy metals in contaminated soils. Journal of Cleaner Production, 2024, 450: 141906. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 10.2) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jclepro.2024.141906
6. Yi Wu, Zongwei Wang, Yuhang Yan, Yuqian Zhou, Ziyu Xue, Bushra Huma, Zhongxin Tan* and Tuo Zhou. Effect of granulated biochar sphere on mineral nutrients in removing potentially toxic elements from contaminated agricultural soils. Science of the Total Environment, 2024, 949: 174775. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 8.6) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.scitotenv.2024.174775
7. Yuqian Zhou, Yuwei Hu, Zhongxin Tan* and Tuo Zhou. Cellulose extraction from rice straw waste for biodegradable ethyl cellulose films preparation using green chemical technology. Journal of Cleaner Production, 2024, 439: 140839. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 10.2) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jclepro.2024.140839
8. Yuqian Zhou and Zhongxin Tan*. Management of soft rot in pakchoi (Brassica chinensis L.) using polyphenols from pineapple peel waste. Journal of Environmental Chemical Engineering, 2024, 12: 114342. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 7.3) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jece.2024.114342
9. Yuqian Zhou, Zhongxin Tan* and Tuo Zhou. Pyrolysis pretreatment and low-temperature liquefaction: Developing rice straw biochar-based clean liquid biofuel. Journal of the Energy Institute, 2024, 117: 101710. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 5.4) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.joei.2024.101710
10. Shengnan Yuan, Tuo Zhou. and Zhongxin Tan*. New Straw Coating Material for Improving the Slow-Release Performance of Fertilizers. ACS Applied Materials & Interfaces, 2023, 15: 39818-39826. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 8.8) https://doi.org/10.1021/acsami.3c06408
11. Yuqian Zhou, Bushra Huma and Zhongxin Tan*. High-Value Utilization of Polyphenol Aromatic Antimicrobial Agents Extracted from Pineapple Peel Waste. ACS Food Science & Technology, 2023, 3: 858-865. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 2.6) https://doi.org/10.1021/acsfoodscitech.3c00048
12. Zongwei Wang, Zhongxin Tan*, Hui Li, Shengnan Yuan, Ying Zhang and Yifan Dong. Direct current electrochemical method for removal and recovery of heavy metals from water using straw biochar electrode. Journal of Cleaner Production, 2022, 339: 130746. (通讯作者, 2025 IF: 10.2) https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jclepro.2022.130746

